.htm |date=12 April 2008 }}</ref> (missing wreck) |- | FV || [[FV Jutland|Jutland]] || style="text-align:center;"|1920 || approximately 160 kilometers southeast of [[Halifax, Nova Scotia|Halifax]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/details/canadianfisherma07cana}}</ref> |- |} |} |} |}
