316202136/http://www.memorials.inportsmouth.co.uk/churches/st_anns/atalanta.htm |date=16 March 2008 }}</ref> |- valign="top" |SS ||''[[SS City of Boston|City of Boston]]''|| style="text-align:center;"|1870|| somewhere between [[New York City]] and [[Liverpool]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" |SS ||[[SS City of Glasgow|''City of Glasgow'']]|| style="text-align:center;"|1854|| somewhere between [[Liverpool]] and [[Philadelphia]]<ref name="nalosses">{{cite web |url=http://www.theshipslist.com/ships/Wrecks/nalosses.htm |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2008-03-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429022634/http://www.theshipslist.com/ships/Wrecks/nalosses.htm |archivedate=29 April 2008 |df=dmy-all }} North Atlantic passenger steamship losses 1841 to 1978</ref> |- valign="top" | ||''City of Limerick''|| style="text-align:center;"|1882|| somewhere between [[New York City]] and [[London]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''City of London''|| style="text-align:center;"|1881|| somewhere between [[London]] and [[New York City]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Colombo''|| style="text-align:center;"|1876|| somewhere between [[Kingston upon Hull|Hull]] and [[New York City]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" |USS ||[[USS Epervier (1814)|''Epervier'']]|| style="text-align:center;"|1815|| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.history.navy.mil/danfs/e4/epervier.htm|title=Epervier|author=|date=|website=navy.mil|accessdate=31 May 2018}}</ref> |- valign="top" | ||''Erin''|| style="text-align:center;"|1889|| somewhere between [[New York City]] and [[London]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Henry Edye'' || style="text-align:center;"|1881|| somewhere between [[Antwerp]] and [[New York City]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Hermann Ludwig'' || style="text-align:center;"|1878|| somewhere between [[New York City]] and [[Antwerp]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Humber''|| style="text-align:center;"|188