urse" /> |- valign="top" |MS ||[[MS München|''München'']] || style="text-align:center;"|1978|| somewhere around {{Coord|44|N|24|W}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seefunknetz.de/deat.htm|title=Seefunkstelle Lashcarrier München / DEAT|first=Heinrich|last=Busch|date=|website=www.seefunknetz.de|accessdate=31 May 2018}}</ref> (missing wreck) |- valign="top" |SS ||[[SS Naronic|''Naronic'']]|| style="text-align:center;"|1893|| somewhere between Point Lynas, [[Wales]] and [[New York City]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||[[Neustria (ship)|''Neustria'']] || style="text-align:center;"|1908|| somewhere between [[New York City]] and [[Marseille]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Neva''|| style="text-align:center;"|1887 ||somewhere between [[Banyuwangi]] and [[Lisbon]]<ref name="nourse" /> (also listed under ''Indian Ocean'') |- valign="top" | ||[[Pacific (Collins Line ship)|''Pacific'']] || style="text-align:center;"|1856|| somewhere between [[Liverpool]] and [[New York City]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Pauillac''|| style="text-align:center;"|1900|| somewhere between [[Glasgow]] and [[St. John, New Brunswick]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''President''|| style="text-align:center;"|1841|| somewhere between [[New York City]] and [[Liverpool]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''De Ruyter''|| style="text-align:center;"|1894|| somewhere between [[Antwerp]] and [[New York City]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Shannon''|| style="text-align:center;"|1872|| somewhere between [[Montreal]] and [[Liverpool]]<ref name="nalosses" /> |- valign="top" | ||''Shannon''|| style="text-align:center;"|1885 ||somewhere between [[London]] and [[Calcutta]]<ref name="nourse" /> (also listed under ''Indian Ocean'') |- valign="top" | ||[[Spray (sailing vessel)|''Spray'']]|| style="text-align:center;"|1909||somewhere between [[Vineyard Haven]], United States and [[Venezuela]]<ref>[http://www.smallcraftadvisor.com/seaworthiness.ht