{{Orphan|date=August 2018}}

The '''modem tax''' is a [[hoax]] dating back to the days of [[bulletin board system]]s stating the [[Federal Communication Commission]] or the [[United States Congress]] intends to impose a tax on [[modem]] use.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snopes.com/inboxer/pending/internet2.asp|title=FACT CHECK: Internet Access Charges|website=Snopes.com|accessdate=28 July 2018}}</ref> The FCC has described it as an [[urban myth]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://urbanlegends.about.com/library/blfcc.htm|title=73 Computer-Related Terms in Spanish You Should Learn|website=Urbanlegends.about.com|accessdate=28 July 2018}}</ref>

